title: I did not get the birthday poro icon
body: I got the Riot Kayle skin but not the birthday poro icon . All of my friends got this special icon but i still didnt get it.

replies.body: It's good to hear your friends have received there gifts, but there are a lot of accounts who are eligible so the process is not finished.  Stay up to date at our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until this is all wrapped up!
